                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Abilità elementale</span></p><p></p><p>Infligge 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">DAN da Electro</span>, invoca 1 <span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Oz</span>.</p>",
